  <acronym>SOKO-1</acronym>
  <official_title>&quot;Fight-or-flight&quot; Versus &quot;Tend-and-befriend&quot; Response to Behavioral and Pharmacological Interventions in Patients With Borderline Personality Disorder - Part I</official_title>
